docs.checks: The `checks` flake output contains derivations that will be built by `nix flake check`.
docs.overlays:
The `overlays` flake output defines "overlays" that can be plugged into Nixpkgs.
Overlays add additional packages or modify or replace existing packages.
docs.packages: The `packages` flake output contains packages that can be added to a shell using `nix shell`.
